It&#x27;s getting hit because you&#x27;re running on Windows/Mac and Windows/Mac specific methods are calling it.  In platform generic code like OutputDevices.cpp you see this:<p><pre><code>    #if PLATFORM_EXCEPTIONS_DISABLED
    		FPlatformMisc::DebugBreak();
    #else
		FPlatformMisc::RaiseException( 1 );
    #endif</code></pre>
